{"tid":1167350,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[殺神加入]奇洛李維斯加入Toy Story4","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T05:32:40.000Z","uid":34409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7c4570c1d6c14d989d25a95a4c42c112645e2f","tid":1167350,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"以下文章來自巴哈<br />\n<br />\n最新官方預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RA-11WlGGkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRA-11WlGGkE&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=b08f75bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RA-11WlGGkE</a><br />\n<br />\n 迪士尼皮克斯動畫電影《Toy Story 4》近日發布了最終版預告宣傳影片，作品 6 月 20 日在台上映。<br />\n <br />\n  《Toy Story 4》故事發生在安弟離家展開大學生涯，玩具們輾轉來到愛惜玩具的小女孩邦妮家中。某天，邦妮帶來了一個手作新成員「叉奇」加入玩具們，本身為拋棄式餐具的叉奇認為自己不是玩具，而是垃圾，因而引發了不少混亂。在一場冒險旅程之後，胡迪警長與老友牧羊女重逢，發現外面玩具們的世界，遠比他想像的還要巨大&hellip;&hellip;。作品由《Inside Out》片頭短片《萊莉的第一次約會》導演喬許科雷執導。<br />\n<br />\n 參與作品配音的演員除了湯姆&middot;漢克斯（飾演胡迪）、提姆&middot;艾倫（飾演巴斯光年）、瓊安&middot;庫薩克（飾演翠絲）&hellip;&hellip;等人之外，還有基努&middot;李維（飾演卡蹦公爵）、托尼&middot;海爾（飾演叉奇）、克莉絲汀娜&middot;漢卓克斯（飾演 GABBY）等新角色登場。"},{"pid":"c92367c1055387bde51318f6aa94c0f6ef396b1f","tid":1167350,"uid":156511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"殺L晒胡迪巴斯直接完左呢個系列"},{"pid":"4f9bec5d1a885a867c2d2af8096fde3abb365247","tid":1167350,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-cuLcPB2fxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-cuLcPB2fxA&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=946104a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-cuLcPB2fxA</a><br />\n<br />\n奇洛李維斯做你情敵"},{"pid":"3849daf0c707bb5ed3bf4acb3ad63e2b7cef67ec","tid":1167350,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9bec5d1a885a867c2d2af8096fde3abb365247","tid":1167350,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,